name: Celcob
overview: Celcob develops a mobile app for time & expense tracking. It helps you track and bill all the time you incurred in daily activities as a professional, enterprise or person. It’s an application for smartphones and tablets that helps measure the time dedicated in routine tasks, such as calls, emails, SMS, expenses, meetings, etc. All the data is secured in Celcob cloud servers and can be access through the app or the web site. You can review all your tagged activities through reports that can be generate from the app in two different ways: a) as a summary of all your activities displayed in the smartphone, or b) as an Excel report send directly to your email. Celcob Activity Tracker is a perfect solution in terms of organization. It’s developed for today’s professionals seeking mobile tools to help them increase efficiency, effectiveness and generate value.
